Description: The Flight into Egypt, with Mary on the donkey, a facsimile of a drawing by Hoogstraten Etching with aquatint
Curator's comments: After the drawing now in the Museum of Fine Arts, Budapest (Sumowski 1190*) from the Kollowrath collection.
Bibliographic references: Hollstein / Dutch and Flemish etchings, engravings and woodcuts c.1450-1700 (14) (after Hoogstraten)
